
     A Single Tone, CTCSS, DCS, SELCALL, DTMF, 2 TONE And VOICE Encoder.
     -------------------------------------------------------------------


    Minimum Requirements:-
    ----------------------

    1) A Standard A600HD, (A500+ with a HDD).
    2) OS 2.0x.
    3) OCS.
    4) A B&W PAL/NTSC television set.
    5) An extra floppy disk drive ONLY if no HD is fitted.
    6) The mouse is OPTIONAL.
    7) The software has NOT been tested on Workbench 1.3x or less.
    8) The software has NOT been tested on Workbench 3.1x or greater.
    9) It has been THOROUGHLY tested on WinUAE, See ~WinUAE~ drawer.
   10) Very high quality, calibrated, RF signal source.
   11) ALL standard, libraries, devices, fonts, handlers and commands.
   12) ~translator.library~, ~speak-handler~ and ~narrator.device~
       are required. Alternatively ~translator42.lha~ can be used from
       AMINET in the ~util/libs~ drawer, (C)1995 Francesco Devitt.
   13) ~More~, ~Display~ and ~LHA~ are also required.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

    General Information:-
    ---------------------

    This tool is an Audio Encoder to generate the necessary codes for
    professional business two way radios. It is just as good for the
    professional RF engineer as well as for the AMATEUR enthusiast.
    The modes generated are CTCSS, DCS, SELCALL, DTMF, 2TONE, VOICE,
    CONTINUOUS SINGLE TONE and ALL OFF with mixtures of these.

